vote.title: Authorize a three-year Interlocal Agreement between the University of North Texas at Dallas and Dallas Water Utilities through the Caruth Police Institute at the University of North Texas at Dallas to provide civilian leadership training for all staff in the field of government for the period October 25, 2023 through October 25, 2026 - Not to exceed $529,000.00 - Financing: Dallas Water Utilities Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
